snippet.title: Crystal Comet announcement trailer
snippet.description:
Team up with your squad & take on the galaxy in this frantic twin stick space shooter "Squad em' up". 
Play single player with the AI or local co-op with your friends!

Coming soon to Steam.

Wesbsite: https://crystal-comet.manakeep.com/

Store page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2642920/Crystal_Comet/

A game by RewdanSprites. 
Music by Paul Michael Kixx. (also music in game).
Level background designs by Mavy Orion. 
Trailer thumbnail & marketing art by Curz Blayz.
